---
title: Cantina-Style Steak Quesadillas with Rice, Black Beans & Charred Corn Salsa
description: This loaded steak quesadilla dinner has something for everyone. Inside each golden tortilla, you’ll find a blend of melty Mexican cheeses and bites of juicy Fajita-spiced steak, and on the side, you’ll serve rice, simmered beans, and a corn salsa. Don’t forget about toppings: Guacamole, sour cream, scallions, and hot sauce complete the meal!
